          "o">=</span><span class="s">&#34;--d:block; --d-md:none&#34;</span><span class="p"></span><span class="p">&gt;</span>Only visible on small screens<span class=
          "p">&lt;</span><span class="p">/</span><span class="nt">button</span><span class="p">&gt;</span></code></pre>
